{%- comment -%}
  Shelzy's Designs - Enhanced Navigation Header

  Features:
  - Logo left, cart right
  - Simplified nav: Shop All, Weddings & Bridesmaids, Kids & Sports, Corporate, Holiday, FAQ
  - Mega menu dropdowns
  - Mobile hamburger menu

